{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "adopt-ai-collection-v3",
		"name": "AdOpt AI - Full API Documentation",
		"description": "## 🚀 AdOpt AI Platform API\n\nWelcome to the AdOpt AI API documentation. This collection provides a comprehensive set of requests to interact with the AdOpt AI backend.\n\n### 🔴 CRITICAL: Fixing the 401 Unauthorized Error\nIf you see `\"message\": \"Not authorized, no token\"`, it means you haven't logged in yet. \n\n**Follow these steps to solve ALL problems:**\n1.  **Register**: Go to `1. Authentication > Register User`. Hit **Send**. (This saves your token automatically).\n2.  **Login**: Go to `1. Authentication > Login`. Hit **Send**. (This also saves/updates your token automatically).\n3.  **Run other APIs**: Now you can hit `Create Campaign`, `Get Insights`, etc. They will automatically use the saved token.\n\n### 🛠️ Configuration\n- `baseUrl`: `http://localhost:5000/api` (Default)\n- `token`: Managed automatically by the Test Scripts in Login/Register requests.\n\n### 🔐 Authentication\nThe collection uses **Bearer Token** authentication inherited from the root level. Ensure each request has **Authorization: Inherit auth from parent** selected (it is by default).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Authentication",
			"description": "User account management. Run Login/Register first to populate the `token` variable.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register User",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Token saved successfully!\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"Hemang\",\n    \"email\": \"hemang@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"register"
							]
						}
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Token saved successfully!\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"hemang@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						}
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
